Detailed Description

Nimu_CppiDescCfg.

Structure to specify the CPPI descriptor configuration for a NIMU free queue used to hold pre-allocated buffers.

Field Documentation

uint32_t _Nimu_CppiDescCfg::descMemRegion

CPPI Memory region to be used for this set of free descriptors.

Size of CPPI free descriptors to allocate

Cppi_DescType _Nimu_CppiDescCfg::descType

CPPI Descriptor Type.

Valid values are: Cppi_DescType_HOST, Cppi_DescType_MONOLITHIC
